description:
What happens when you build a billion-dollar music empire, but lose yourself along the way? Music mogul Scooter Braun reveals the raw truth behind his mask.

Scooter Braun is a renowned music executive, entrepreneur, and manager behind the careers of global stars like Justin Bieber, Ariana Grande, Kanye West, Taylor Swift, Demi Lovato, J Balvin and more He is CEO of HYBE America and founder of SB Projects, a dynamic entertainment and media company.

In this conversation, Scooter shares:
â—½ï¸ The mask he wore as â€œScooterâ€ and the journey back to being Scott
â—½ï¸ Why he carries guilt for every young artist he managed
â—½ï¸ How 20 years of running finally led him to confront his deepest fears
â—½ï¸ Why he felt like a complete fraud even at the top
â—½ï¸ The reason why his divorce saved his life

No conditions. No pre-approved questions. Just an unfiltered conversation about everything.

â€”
